<br />
<br />
It's been a couple years since I played on the PvP servers... so this may no longer work... but try getting a Bioluminesent Orb and spamming it on the pet until it lands, then shadow step away, then nuke him.  Never waste nukes on the pet, that's a sure way to loose.  Also, go get a dispell clicky  from Ssra or Fear, and use it to strip all his buffs, that's about your only chance.</div>
	</td>
